 0;"><li style=3D"margin: 8px 0 0 32px;"><p style=3D"box-sizing: border-box=
; color: rgb(54, 55, 55); font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0; ma=
rgin-bottom: 0; padding-left: 4px;"><strong>Mean-reversion bubble</strong><=
span>:&#160; &#8220;the basic bet is that the future will continue along pr=
esent trends.&#8221; Think: the mortgage crisis. If you bet that the future=
